This white paper builds on decades of work by scientists, engineers, economists, and policy experts across government, industry, and academia. While representing an integrated strategic vision, it stands on the shoulders of:

- NASA's Moon to Mars architecture studies
- ESA's Lunar Gateway and Mars exploration planning
- Industry feasibility studies from SpaceX, Blue Origin, and others
- Academic research on closed-loop life support, ISRU, and space economics
- International legal scholarship on space resource governance

We are grateful to all who have advanced humanity's path to becoming a multiplanetary civilization.

